snippet.title: Johnny Depp's Lawyer Exposed Amber Heard And Elon Musk's Private Texts
snippet.description:
In this video we’ll talk about How Johnny Depp's Lawyer Exposed Amber Heard And Elon Musk's Private Texts. 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
___________________________________________

Amber Heard texted with SpaceX billionaire Elon Musk several days before she filed for divorce from Johnny Depp, and it's clear from the exchange the SpaceX boss is hoping to be more than just friends...texting the actress, "I really like you."

A transcript of the text messages, turned over in the 'Aquaman' stars ongoing lawsuit with Depp, was just tweeted publicly by the 'Pirates Of The Caribbean' star's lawyer Adam Waldman. 

Inspired By Amber Heard And Elon Musk's private texts exposed by johnny depp's lawyer.
